  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Economy Village View Rooms</strong> are around 15m<span>² sleeping two people. These rooms have twin beds, and a North facing view of the village.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Double Matterhorn View Rooms</strong> are around 22m² sleeping two to three people. These rooms have a double bed, and space for an additional bed plus a balcony with South facing views of the Matterhorn.</span></p>
<p><strong>Single Village View Rooms</strong> sleep one and are around 13m² with a single bed, shower and a North facing view of the village - some rooms may have a balcony. </p>
<p><strong><span>Junior Village View Suites</span></strong> are around 31m² and sleep two to four people. These rooms have twin beds, and a lounge area with a sliding door which can accommodate two additional beds. These rooms have a balcony with North facing views of the village. Suitable for two adults and two children, or three adults. These rooms are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call if you would like to book this room type.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Minibar </li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
